---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Contribute — OpenInterstate">
  <section>
    <h1>Contribute</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Naming review, schema review, release-shape review, examples, and
      documentation clarity are the most useful early contributions.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Repos</h2>
    <ul class="links">
      <li><a href="https://github.com/tldev/openinterstate">github.com/tldev/openinterstate</a> — main project</li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/tldev/openinterstate-reachability">github.com/tldev/openinterstate-reachability</a> — drive-time reachability scores between interstate exits and nearby POIs</li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/tldev/openinterstate.org">github.com/tldev/openinterstate.org</a> — this site</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Current focus</h2>
    <p>Lock names, publish the data contract, ship the first release.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
